item.description: Changelog # All notable changes to this project are documented in this page. The format is based on Keep a Changelog. 1.0.0-beta.3 - 2023-06-13 # If you’re using v0.3.x or older, Please upgrade to v0.4.x before upgrading v1.x.x! もし v0.3.x 以前を使用しているのであれば, v1.x.xに更新する前に v0.4.x に更新してください! Added # Merged changes in 0.4.7 #224 0.4.7 - 2023-06-13 # Fixed # Dropping PhysBone to MergePhysBone is not working #221 First box will be size of zero #223 1.
